tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE sentiment_analysis_data (
  transcript_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  transcript_text TEXT,
  sentiment_score FLOAT,
  support_team_feedback TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE support_performance (
    performance_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    team_id INT,
    transcript_id INT,
    performance_score FLOAT,
    FOREIGN KEY (team_id) REFERENCES support_team(team_id),
    FOREIGN KEY (transcript_id) REFERENCES voice_transcripts(transcript_id)
);

CREATE TABLE VoiceTranscripts (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    transcript_text TEXT,
    transcription_date TIMESTAMP,
    speaker_id INT,
    sentiment_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE voice_transcripts (
    transcript_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    transcript_text TEXT,
    sentiment_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE support_team (
    team_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    team_name TEXT,
    team_lead_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE support_tickets (
    ticket_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    transcript_id INT,
    team_id INT,
    ticket_status TEXT
)

CREATE TABLE team_members (
    member_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    member_name TEXT,
    team_id INT
)

CREATE TABLE sentiment_analysis (
    analysis_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    transcript_id INT,
    sentiment_category TEXT,
    sentiment_score FLOAT
)
